00:19.541 --> 00:22.974
He hasn't filed anything:
Louisiana, Maryland.

00:22.974 --> 00:24.677
Well, at least he's not padding

00:24.677 --> 00:27.413
All he's put in for
are a few local dinners.

00:27.413 --> 00:30.309
And those he charged
to the photo desk.

00:30.309 --> 00:34.877
- Come again?
- On Katya Jalenak's card. Not his.

00:37.641 --> 00:40.979
Thank you, Edwards.
Um, I'll talk to him.

00:40.979 --> 00:45.308
And, uh, you'll keep this
between us?

00:48.266 --> 00:54.313
Me and Carl? Mr. Elkins, there's
nothing going on between me...

00:54.313 --> 00:57.624
No one needs to know.
No one needs to lose her job.

00:57.624 --> 00:59.694
It just has to end.

01:02.999 --> 01:08.616
Don't tell me that!
They're going to crucify me.

01:08.616 --> 01:12.954
We'll talk about this after I get home.
After you send the ne...

01:12.954 --> 01:15.708
You cannot stop now!

01:23.939 --> 01:26.637
- Same thing?
- Ben!

01:26.637 --> 01:32.348
I'm almost there. I'm just waitin' 
to hear from two sources.

01:32.348 --> 01:37.062
We will crush the Times.
Trust me.

01:40.420 --> 01:42.052
You've got a file.

01:44.000 --> 01:50.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:52.167 --> 01:57.041
No! No.

01:58.210 --> 02:01.802
By seeking truth, by shedding light...

02:01.802 --> 02:04.812
all of you are truly winners.

02:08.652 --> 02:11.431
- Tough act to follow, Mr. Elkins.
- Thank you.

02:12.517 --> 02:14.863
Ben, terrific speech.

02:14.863 --> 02:17.609
- Sure, Roy, thanks.
- Everything okay?

02:17.609 --> 02:20.506
I'm, uh...
I'm up against it here, Roy.

02:24.031 --> 02:26.073
You little son of a bitch.

02:32.176 --> 02:37.165
Carl?
Carl, is that you?

02:39.857 --> 02:41.590
What was that?

02:41.590 --> 02:45.523
Come on. Let's go
make our own noise.

02:49.367 --> 02:54.557
No! Don't! No... Stop!

